==English==
===Etymology===
From Middle English for "God be with [[ye]]"

===Pronunciation===
*[[w:AHD|AHD]]: go͝odbīʹ
*[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /gʊdˈbaɪ/
*[[w:SAMPA|SAMPA]]: /<tt>gUd"baI</tt>/

===Interjection===
'''goodbye'''
#[[farewell]]; a formula used to another person or persons when the speaker or writer is [[depart]]ing.

